A signal handler for a signal generated from a call to raise or abort calls the raise function:
      > in raise at UB-SIGNAL2-bad.c:4:13
        in handler at UB-SIGNAL2-bad.c:4:13
        in raise at UB-SIGNAL2-bad.c:10:7
        in main at UB-SIGNAL2-bad.c:10:7

    Undefined behavior (UB-SIGNAL2):
        see C11 section 7.14.1.1:4 http://rvdoc.org/C11/7.14.1.1
        see C11 section J.2:1 item 131 http://rvdoc.org/C11/J.2
        see CERT-C section SIG33-C http://rvdoc.org/CERT-C/SIG33-C

